**Two-wheeler loans** finance new motorcycles, scooters, and electric vehicles. Banks and NBFCs offer up to 95% of the on-road price at rates ranging from 9% p.a. (for salaried borrowers at major banks) to 28% p.a. at dealer-arranged financing. For electric two-wheelers, some state governments offer additional subsidies.
